&gt; I am crawling a list of seed urls with a depth of 5. However, the seed report file has not been changed for five days. Although the size of the crawled document is increasing, the number of seed urls that are not crawled does not decrease. I suspect the crawler might be &quot;trapped&quot; into a website so I want the crawler to stop crawling the current seed urls and simply start crawling the remaining seed URLs. How can I do that? I am using H3.1.0. Thanks. -John
